OL,3,CChris Thomas sacked from Manx health
OL,4,Cdepartment after two and a half weeks
OL,6,FA backbench politician has been sacked
OL,7,Ffrom his role within the Isle of Man's
OL,8,Fhealth service, two and a half weeks
OL,9,Fafter taking on the job.
OL,11,FChris Thomas MHK lost his role as a
OL,12,Fpolitical member within the Department
OL,13,Fof Health and Social Care (DHSC),
OL,14,Fafter voting against Alfred Cannan MHK
OL,15,Fin a recent vote of no confidence
OL,16,Fagainst his leadership.
OL,18,FHe was assigned to the DHSC on Friday
OL,19,F18 October, but has been let go by the
OL,20,FChief Minister.
