OL,3,CChris Thomas sacked from Manx health
OL,4,Cdepartment after two and a half weeks
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Thomas said: "It is
OL,7,Fridiculous to think I should resign as
OL,8,Fa backbench departmental member a week
OL,9,Fafter accepting Health Minister
OL,10,FCannan's invitation to use my 'wealth
OL,11,Fof experience' to help him 'to make
OL,12,Frapid progress in reviewing the Manx
OL,13,FCare mandate alongside the associated
OL,14,Fbudget requirements', as Mr Cannan put
OL,15,Fit on 18 October.
OL,17,F"My views on Government and the Island
OL,18,FPlan were clear, and Mr Cannan knew I
OL,19,Fhad no intention to become his next
OL,20,FMinister", he added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
