OL,3,CChris Thomas sacked from Manx health
OL,4,Cdepartment after two and a half weeks
OL,6,F"Given my role as acting Minister for
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care, Mr Thomas has
OL,8,Fdirectly undermined that relationship
OL,9,Fand ethically Mr Thomas should have
OL,10,Fresigned from his role in the
OL,11,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,12,Fwhen he undertook these actions.
OL,14,F"I am sure Mr Thomas understands this
OL,15,Fposition and I hope he can continue to
OL,16,Ffind a way to support the work of the
OL,17,FGovernment going forward."
OL,19,FMr Thomas not only voted against Mr
OL,20,FCannan, but also put himself forward
OL,21,Fas the next Chief Minister.
