OL,6,FHowever, the motion failed after 18
OL,7,FMHKs voted to support Mr Cannan,
OL,8,Fcompared to six who voted against him.
OL,10,FMr Thomas said: "Since then I have
OL,11,Fmade a positive and productive
OL,12,Fcontribution in the department, & Mr
OL,13,FCannan did not mention any issues this
OL,14,Flast 10 days in various meetings &
OL,15,Fother situations. CoMin seemed to have
OL,16,Foverruled his departmental invitation,
OL,17,For perhaps the next Health Minister
OL,18,Fwanted me gone."
